OL,3,CMan, 36, to appear in court after
OL,4,Cpedestrians hit by car in Derby
OL,6,FA 36-year-old man is due to appear in
OL,7,Fcourt accused of dangerous driving
OL,8,Fafter seven people were injured when a
OL,9,Fcar hit pedestrians in Derby.
OL,11,FSandhu Ponnachan, of Chariot Close,
OL,12,FAlvaston, has also been charged with
OL,13,Fsix counts of causing grievous bodily
OL,14,Fharm with intent, one count of
OL,15,Fattempted grievous bodily harm, and
OL,16,Fone count of possession of a bladed
OL,17,Farticle, Derbyshire Police said on
OL,18,FTuesday night.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
