PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775009000
OL,3,CMan, 36, to appear in court after
OL,4,Cpedestrians hit by car in Derby
OL,6,FThe victims were four men and three
OL,7,Fwomen aged between 36 and 52, and four
OL,8,Fhave been discharged from hospital,
OL,9,FDerbyshire Police said.
OL,11,FTheir injuries have been described by
OL,12,Fpolice as not life-threatening.
OL,14,FPonnachan, who is originally from
OL,15,FIndia but now lives in Derby, was
OL,16,Farrested seven minutes after the
OL,17,Fincident.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
