CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775009000
OL,3,CMan, 36, to appear in court after
OL,4,Cpedestrians hit by car in Derby
OL,6,FChief Superintendent Emma Aldred said
OL,7,Fin a statement on Tuesday night: "This
OL,8,Fincident has, naturally, sent
OL,9,Fshockwaves through the community of
OL,10,FDerby and the county as a whole.
OL,12,F"My thoughts, and those of the wider
OL,13,Fforce, remain with each of the seven
OL,14,Finjured people, their families, and
OL,15,Fwitnesses at the scene.
OL,26,@oD@bOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775009000
OL,3,CMan, 36, to appear in court after
OL,4,Cpedestrians hit by car in Derby
OL,6,F"I would like to reiterate my thanks
OL,7,Fto all the people that have assisted
OL,8,Four investigation ` the public,
OL,9,Fpartner agencies, local businesses and
OL,10,Falso the media and wider community for
OL,11,Ftheir patience and understanding as we
OL,12,Fhave worked to seek a charge.
OL,14,F"While today's charge is positive
OL,15,Fnews, and one that I hope brings a
OL,16,Fdegree of reassurance, the
OL,17,Finvestigation into the incident
OL,18,Fcontinues and I would once again
OL,19,Fappeal for anyone who has any
OL,20,Finformation to come forward.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775009000
OL,3,CMan, 36, to appear in court after
OL,4,Cpedestrians hit by car in Derby
OL,6,F"As a final word, now that charges
OL,7,Fhave been made I'd ask for the
OL,8,Fcooperation of the public to allow the
OL,9,Fjudicial process to continue without
OL,10,Fany speculation online or elsewhere
OL,11,Fthat could impede the pursuit of
OL,12,Fjustice for all those affected."
OL,14,FJanine McKinney, of the Crown
OL,15,FProsecution Service, said: "Our
OL,16,Fprosecutors have worked to establish
OL,17,Fthat there is sufficient evidence to
OL,18,Fbring the case to court and that it is
OL,19,Fin the public interest to pursue
OL,20,Fcriminal proceedings.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@`O]wD@\OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775009000
OL,3,CMan, 36, to appear in court after
OL,4,Cpedestrians hit by car in Derby
OL,6,F"We have worked carefully with
OL,7,FDerbyshire Police as they carried out
OL,8,Ftheir investigation."
OL,10,FDerbyshire Police are asking anyone
OL,11,Fwith footage of the incident to
OL,12,Fcontact them.
OL,14,FThe force previously said the support
OL,15,Fof counter-terrorism officers does not
OL,16,Fmean the incident is being treated as
OL,17,Fterrorism.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@UO]
